definition: Dazu suburban county in Chongqing municipality, formerly in Sichuan
big/huge/large/major/great/wide/deep/older (than)/oldest/eldest/greatly/very much/(dialect) father/father's elder or younger brother

sentences.english: Dazu County, located in the southeast of Sichuan province, is 271 kilometres away from Chengdu and 163 kilometres away from Chongqing.
sentences.chinese: 大足縣在重慶市的西北，縣城距重慶百餘公里。

sentences.english: In Dazu County, Mr Long is an authority on bees and generating higher amounts of honey.
sentences.chinese: 在大足縣，龍先生是養蜂專家，蜂蜜產量高於同行。
